---
import ModuleLayout from '../../layouts/ModuleLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../../lib/utils';
---

<ModuleLayout moduleId="zhou" title="时间">
  <div class="zhou-overview">
    <section class="intro-section">
      <h2>时间长河之流</h2>
      <p>宙者，古往今来之谓也。时间如河，因果如链。轮回之道，起于前世终于来生。修行者欲知命数，必先明时间之理。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="features-grid">
      <a href={withBase('/zhou/reincarnation')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔄</div>
        <h3>轮回查询</h3>
        <p>前世今生因果</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/zhou/calendar-system')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📅</div>
        <h3>纪年系统</h3>
        <p>多纪元时间转换</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/zhou/eras')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⏳</div>
        <h3>时代划分</h3>
        <p>各时代浏览</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/zhou/timeline')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>时间线</h3>
        <p>大事年表</p>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="knowledge-section">
      <h2>时间知识</h2>
      <div class="knowledge-grid">
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>轮回六道</h3>
          <p>天道、人道、阿修罗道、畜生道、饿鬼道、地狱道。修行者超脱六道，方能归于大道。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>因果律</h3>
          <p>种瓜得瓜，种豆得豆。善恶有报，时候未到。轮回转世，皆循因果。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>纪年之法</h3>
          <p>天干地支六十甲子循环，修行界以灵气潮汐为纪，世俗以朝代更迭为纪。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .zhou-overview { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .intro-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: rgba(240, 64, 128, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 64, 128, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; }
    .intro-section h2 { color: #f04080; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .intro-section p { color: #888; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .feature-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 64, 128, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #f04080; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(240, 64, 128, 0.15); }
    .card-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { color: #f0d8e8; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; }
    .feature-card p { color: #888; margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .knowledge-section h2 { color: #f04080; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .knowledge-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .knowledge-card { padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 64, 128, 0.1); border-radius: 6px; }
    .knowledge-card h3 { color: #f04080; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; }
    .knowledge-card p { color: #aaa; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</ModuleLayout>
